<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8254914>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Tirmilyra sagittifera (Alcock, 1896) n. comb., lectotype male (CL 5.0 mm, CW 4.5 mm) (ZSI C910/10), Karachi, Pakistan: (A) maxilliped 3; (B) pleon. Tirmilyra concinnus (Ghani & Tirmizi, 1995) n. comb., fresh specimen male (CL 8.4 mm, CW 7.6 mm) (ZUTC 6925) Hormoz Island, Persian Gulf: (C) maxilliped 3; (D) pleon." ;
