<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8254918>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Tirmilyra sagittifera (Alcock, 1896) n. comb., lectotype male male (CL 5.0 mm, CW 4.5 mm) (ZSI C910/10), Karachi, Pakistan: (A) G1 shaft; (B) G1 tip; Tirmilyra sagittifera (Alcock, 1896) n. comb., fresh specimen male (CL 4.2 mm, CW 3.9 mm) (ZMUC CRU885), Bushehr, Iran, Persian Gulf: (C) G1 shaft; (D) G1 tip; Tirmilyra concinnus (Ghani & Tirmizi, 1995) n. comb., fresh specimen male (CL 8.4 mm, CW 7.6 mm) (ZUTC 6925) Hormoz Island, Persian Gulf: (E) G1 shaft; (F) G1 tip." ;
